{"tid":2015340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"由今個月開始，我每個月都會儲一萬蚊投資「香港東印度公司」","createTime":"2020-05-13T15:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:45:52.000Z","uid":12633,"like":316,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7d8eed32e26f2d824c10f08da2223b151313f4","tid":2015340,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"前幾日攬炒巴出左兩篇文/錄音，從多條戰線去論述香港可以點樣獨立，包括議會、街頭、國際三條路線等，而且仲可以從各個角度如經濟、文化、姊妹城市⋯⋯去建立香港既國際地位。最近更加有人提出要成立<span style=\"color: gold;\">「香港既東印度公司」</span>，先不論可行性問題，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要知道所有歷史既轉捩點都係由前人一步一步揼石仔揼出黎</span></span>，而香港獨立起碼要用上幾十年以上既時光。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n街頭抗爭呢個階段其實已經冇乜用，搞革命應該搞東印度公司，海外建軍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007554</a> <br />\n<br />\n其實連登有好多人都唔明點解攬炒巴會值中共懸紅追殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2012469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2012469</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n所以我不斷去諗，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我作為一個無咩才能、無議政能力、無演說能力、無社會地位既普通平凡人</span></span>，由今日開始可以做啲咩野去幫香港獨立、香港未來及現在既先驅者們鋪路？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我諗到有兩個微小而隆重既貢獻：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">錢</span></span>。小弟出左黎做野無耐，眼見返工慢慢磨蝕緊自己既軟骨、熱血、青春，好怕再做多幾年前，我就會麻木變成一隻豬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想做啲野，但又發覺返工已經佔用好多時間，721831再去行下街、唱下歌，時間精力就所餘無幾。</span><br />\n去諗自己仲有咩可以貢獻既時候，就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">諗起打工仔最多既就係錢</span> &mdash;&mdash; <span style=\"color: red;\">你犧牲左人格、自由、靈魂換取銀行戶口多一個零，你已經一無所有，你窮得只有錢，你最大可以貢獻既事物就係錢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有一間富可敵國既公司，可以做到啲咩我唔洗講了。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n反正我唔打算買樓、不幸患上重病既話就會直接棄game。儲咁多錢都無咩用，不如all in 落一樣你最想 all in or nothing 既事物？<br />\n<br />\n幫襯黃店、做選民、做文宣、上Twitter、去唱歌行街已經係基本。<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經由上年開始，每個月起碼會儲一萬蚊以上（小弟出黎做野無耐，人工唔高），留俾未來既集資計劃，希望其他平凡既香港人都一樣用你地既辦法做你地做到既事。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">將來如有信得過既香港先驅出現，必定會略盡綿力散盡千金，再用自己條賤命攬炒，只求光復香港。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時希望我會記得呢個post。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，<br />\n唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFrom攬炒巴:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n//攬炒，唔係Burnism，係 Phoenixism，係鳳凰重生 嘅必經過程。香港人，再無同中共妥協嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n但願我地告別犬儒，告別投降，告別內鬥，從此只有重光派，為煲底之約奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵。<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us.//<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"31639aafafe264f4dd0b64c12cbe433f92676d76","tid":2015340,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"［再斷水路］聽講好多狗有秘撈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2015238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2015238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce5f85c848a581461bf51c5928dbf1f1e2d1ed9c","tid":2015340,"uid":170812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"一人儲啲"},{"pid":"77c3d78bac8ef238cb23657fd75fcb54ec19f0cc","tid":2015340,"uid":158955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88e9fd409d29bdcafab39204e553493c21e1dbb","tid":2015340,"uid":351671,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"月供建國，無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n香港獨立唯一出路<br />\n香港再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42557f7e8abc9cce90a932166055562ae58adcf","tid":2015340,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31774fc01475e4d2795077d54aa61854184e59c7","tid":2015340,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:05:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96f911dfef9a69cd6aac73c714926555e97cc44b","tid":2015340,"uid":258578,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:06:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0a0b07aed20adcbd0869f1d10114683c162690b","tid":2015340,"uid":105595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:07:34.000Z","msg":"記得唔好揸死港紙<br />\n分散下貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c310f0c448e1e4d49d1b77854bb31561a1dbaea","tid":2015340,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859f6686fbf413db16f95b2f66a264745bfe7861","tid":2015340,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"0230a4338d2914841ee556c3787ef4c76a4ff47c","tid":2015340,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e671687537b07fbfbe66ccb72fb5748145cbaf9f","tid":2015340,"uid":41855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"我月供冇問題，支持"},{"pid":"c963e02743387a762872c53af4c75559bf730024","tid":2015340,"uid":85065,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"支持，但係名可能要改改，建議golfeto de libereco，官方語言係世界語同廣東話<i