/>\n如果有一間富可敵國既公司，可以做到啲咩我唔洗講了。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n反正我唔打算買樓、不幸患上重病既話就會直接棄game。儲咁多錢都無咩用，不如all in 落一樣你最想 all in or nothing 既事物？<br />\n<br />\n幫襯黃店、做選民、做文宣、上Twitter、去唱歌行街已經係基本。<br />\n<br />\n其實我已經由上年開始，每個月起碼會儲一萬蚊以上（小弟出黎做野無耐，人工唔高），留俾未來既集資計劃，希望其他平凡既香港人都一樣用你地既辦法做你地做到既事。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">將來如有信得過既香港先驅出現，必定會略盡綿力散盡千金，再用自己條賤命攬炒，只求光復香港。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時希望我會記得呢個post。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，<br />\n唯一出路。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFrom攬炒巴:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n//攬炒，唔係Burnism，係 Phoenixism，係鳳凰重生 嘅必經過程。香港人，再無同中共妥協嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n但願我地告別犬儒，告別投降，告別內鬥，從此只有重光派，為煲底之約奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵。<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us.//<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"cf8b76e2ce72a362a47280adbb2064873b1aa2f4","tid":2015340,"uid":287096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"儲錢建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957e739f389570a938e58e87e35981a40343a34f","tid":2015340,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0a0b07aed20adcbd0869f1d10114683c162690b","tid":2015340,"uid":105595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:07:34.000Z","msg":"記得唔好揸死港紙<br />\n分散下貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"c04f449396683abc3272b482611fa5726464fd31","tid":2015340,"uid":265171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698b8df9fdbb81d368fe8d525062c890fa3f7183","tid":2015340,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8474975934031e0674382468358d6427aff862","tid":2015340,"uid":32008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:51:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"儲定錢先，到時就好似管理一間公司咁，由股東&amp;管理層管，而我地應該要有投票權&amp;投票選管理委員會既權力"},{"pid":"c6a9b9f3126f0e9681f2eb793dd175a1a63ae114","tid":2015340,"uid":122270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"大家要email或寫信 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫港台同廣播署長</span><br />\n邊個淨係打個讚啊 推啊 唔email同寫信果d <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"74f524606c1c19dad61e3042d206f7e8f8655ca0","tid":2015340,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d590e9422d005022ae36d3a69314140ac98633de","tid":2015340,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d151b9bb43dc7c6287c2a521e2346bd5f8380199","tid":2015340,"uid":124113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e671687537b07fbfbe66ccb72fb5748145cbaf9f","tid":2015340,"uid":41855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"我月供冇問題，支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"當月供股票<br />\n月供香港未來 抵撚到仆街啦"},{"pid":"c93b8e36922039773d50189bc2ec0eb2df901d27","tid":2015340,"uid":17866,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"搞好管理架構搵到trust 或者其他專業人士接手先好開始科水，唔係等睇腥港歷來最大嘅scam 都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289f0aa178dd8988ce03df65f80d48937ed92868","tid":2015340,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"有冇咁偉大啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5fb2a34760878f7b8a123a76ee40f7884b1b76","tid":2015340,"uid":46759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T10:27:4